{"type":null,"faqId":43495,"title":"如何启用屏幕解锁图案？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>EMUI3.1：设置 &gt; 全部设置 &gt; 隐私和安全 &gt; 锁屏和密码 &gt; 锁屏密码 &gt; 图案密码。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>EMUI3.0及以下版本：设置&gt; 全部设置 &gt; 隐私和安全 &gt; 安全 &gt; 解锁样式 &gt; 图案。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1．请选择图案解锁：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2．在“选择您的图案”界面，通过手指在屏幕连续划过几个圆的圆心设定解锁时使用的图形样式，再点击“继续”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3．再次在屏幕上划过刚才的样式，点击“确认”完成解锁图形的设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4．当点电源键或开关机时，手机会默认进入图案解锁界面，在该界面划过刚才的图案样式，进行解锁。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=151647\" style=\"width:1.7659723in;height:3.1194444in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=151648\" style=\"width:1.74375in;height:3.1194444in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=151649\" style=\"width:1.7548611in;height:3.1194444in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8996","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442399018000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10","visitedTimes":3,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"图案,锁屏","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}